Package org.aksw.cubeqa.benchmark

Sets of questions that form a benchmark to evaluate RDF Data Cube question answering.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Benchmark
    Abstract benchmark class with evaluate function.
    BenchmarkElement
    A single benchmark question along with its correct template.
    FinlandAid
    Benchmark using the LinkedSpending Finland-Aid dataset.
    FinlandAidTest
    Runs the FinlandAid benchmark on the CubeQA algorithm.
